### Tailwind & UI Utilities

- **Tailwind v4**: Classes live in markup; global layer in `src/app/globals.css`.
- **Classnames**: Prefer `clsx` and `tailwind-merge` for conditional classes.
- **Spacing & scales**: Use design tokens from Tailwind defaults; avoid arbitrary values unless necessary.
- **Dark mode**: Use `dark:` variants; avoid inline style overrides.
- **Icons**: Use `lucide-react` components; keep size via Tailwind classes.
- **CVA**: Use `class-variance-authority` to define component variants when needed.
- **Accessibility**: Ensure focus states are visible; use `aria-*` attributes.
